Salim Jreissati: & quot;
01 Nov 2019, 08:27 by Lebanon 24
Minister of State for Presidential Affairs in the caretaker government, Salim Jreissati, tweeted on his own Twitter account, “Well, Riad Koubeissi did on Al Jadeed's screen yesterday to record that there is no corruption in our public career, not because we are waiting for the testimony of No one, but because the forbidden money is genetically ostracized from us and that "they are not all," they preach.
